com.github.kvnxiao.kommandant.command

Class CommandBuilder<T>

  • com.github.kvnxiao.kommandant.command.CommandBuilder<T>

  • public class CommandBuilder<T>

    A builder class that helps define a command without needing to specify all the properties for the class ICommand constructor.

    See Also:
